nagm.title: August Update
nagm.heading: August Update
nagm.body: Welcome back spartans.|n|nThe long promised playlist update is finally here, and more playlists are now working correctly.|nThe following playlists have been fixed.|n|n• Rumble Pit [New!]|n• Big Team Battle|n• Team Slayer|n|nAll maps and gametypes have been recovered for these playlists.|n|nNow that we have more control over the playlists, expect more updates like this going forward.
